# Code owners for llmstatus.io
#
# Syntax: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Order matters — the last matching pattern wins.
#
# The @llmstatus/* GitHub teams must exist in the llmstatus GitHub
# organization. If you rename a team, update this file.

# Default: any change needs maintainer review
*                               @llmstatus/maintainers

# Methodology and public-facing data semantics — operator must approve
/METHODOLOGY.md                 @llmstatus/operators
/docs/ROADMAP.md                @llmstatus/operators

# Brand system — maintainer + design team approval
/docs/brand/                    @llmstatus/maintainers @llmstatus/design

# Governance and conduct — operator approval required
/GOVERNANCE.md                  @llmstatus/operators
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md             @llmstatus/operators
/SECURITY.md                    @llmstatus/operators

# CI / release pipeline
/.github/                       @llmstatus/maintainers
